docs.text: Hello, I am Karimi Zayan I am currently an NSF Firefighter Trainee at SCDF. I was formerly from NUS High School and graduated in 2023 with an honours in Mathematics and Computer Science and Major in Physics and Chemistry. After NS, I will be reading Mathematics and Computer Science at NUS College. I enjoy running, reading, watching movies and playing video games in my free time.
